The Girl In The Spider's Web will be the fourth installment in Millennium crime trilogy by Swedish author Stieg Larsson . 
  It was completed in November by David Lagercrantz based on plot outline left by Larsson before he died of a heart attack in 2004 . 
  The sequel is being written on computers with no internet connection to avoid leaks . 
  It will be published worldwide on August 27 . 
 